OL,3,CDangerous driver rammed into car with
OL,4,Cgrandchildren inside at ice cream shop
OL,6,FA dangerous driver out for ice cream
OL,7,Frammed into a Teesside grandfather's
OL,8,Fcar while his grandchildren sat in the
OL,9,Fvehicle, a court heard.
OL,11,FJason Hackett parked up outside Gelato
OL,12,FJojo, in Seaton Carew, on the evening
OL,13,Fof 2 April, last year.
OL,15,FTeesside Crown Court heard the 31-year-
OL,16,Fold's victim was also parked up on The
OL,17,FFront with his wife and their
OL,18,Fgrandchildren.
