OL,3,CDangerous driver rammed into car with
OL,4,Cgrandchildren inside at ice cream shop
OL,6,FHackett was reportedly making a scene
OL,7,Fand appeared under the influence when
OL,8,Fhis victim offered to get him a taxi
OL,9,Fand tried to stop him driving.
OL,11,FBut the court heard the defendant
OL,12,Fbecame abusive and accelerated away
OL,13,Fbefore reversing at speed into the
OL,14,Fvictim's car.
OL,16,FOn Monday 22 July, Hackett was
OL,17,Fsentenced to 12 months in prison for
OL,18,Fdangerous driving at Teesside Crown
OL,19,FCourt.
