OL,3,CDangerous driver rammed into car with
OL,4,Cgrandchildren inside at ice cream shop
OL,6,FProsecuting the case, Andrew Turton,
OL,7,Fsaid the area was busy with
OL,8,Fpedestrians but Hackett was drawing
OL,9,Fattention to himself while buying ice
OL,10,Fcream.
OL,12,F"He was making a scene of himself and
OL,13,Fhe appeared intoxicated," he said.
OL,15,F"He got in his car and the victim
OL,16,Fapproached the defendant and said
OL,17,F'come on you can't drive like that
OL,18,Fmate, we'll sort you a taxi'."
