OL,3,CDangerous driver rammed into car with
OL,4,Cgrandchildren inside at ice cream shop
OL,6,FThe Middlesbrough court heard the
OL,7,Fdefendant was abusive and, as the
OL,8,Fvictim tried to remove the keys, the
OL,9,Fdefendant drove off with the victim
OL,10,Fstill partly in the window.
OL,12,FOther pedestrians had to move out of
OL,13,Fthe way to avoid being hit during the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FMr Turton said: "After the defendant
OL,17,Faccelerated away at speed he then
OL,18,Freversed at speed towards (the
OL,19,Fvictim's) car, crashing into it with
OL,20,Fhis wife and young grandchildren
OL,21,Fwithin."
