OL,3,CDangerous driver rammed into car with
OL,4,Cgrandchildren inside at ice cream shop
OL,6,FThe court heard the defendant caused
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds worth of damage.
OL,9,FSummarising an impact statement from
OL,10,Fthe victim, Mr Turton said: "He's
OL,11,Fparticularly upset about the affect on
OL,12,Fhis grandchildren, he thought he was
OL,13,Fgoing to be killed.
OL,15,F"This is someone who is reasonably
OL,16,Frobust having served in the Armed
OL,17,FForces."
