OL,3,CDangerous driver rammed into car with
OL,4,Cgrandchildren inside at ice cream shop
OL,6,FThe court heard the defendant has
OL,7,Fconvictions dating back to 2004
OL,8,Fincluding multiple dangerous driving
OL,9,Foffences. He is currently serving an
OL,10,F82-month prison sentence for attempted
OL,11,Frobbery, robbery, and dwelling house
OL,12,Fburglaries.
OL,14,FIn mitigation, the court heard the
OL,15,Fdefendant pleaded guilty to dangerous
OL,16,Fdriving at an earlier hearing on 30
OL,17,FMay and the offence predates the
OL,18,Frobbery and burglary offences.
