OL,3,CDangerous driver rammed into car with
OL,4,Cgrandchildren inside at ice cream shop
OL,6,FAddressing the defendant, Judge
OL,7,FJonathan Carroll said: "You have
OL,8,Fsignificant and relevant previous
OL,9,Fconvictions. You set about the most
OL,10,Fappalling dangerous driving.
OL,12,F"As the victim was leaning into your
OL,13,Fcar you drove off, it was there but
OL,14,Ffor the grace of god that he didn't
OL,15,Ffall under your wheels.
