OL,6,F"You then reversed at speed into the
OL,7,Ffront of his car. You are somebody who
OL,8,Fas well as having a bad record
OL,9,Fgenerally, has three previous
OL,10,Fdangerous driving offences on their
OL,11,Frecord."
OL,13,FThe HMP Northumberland defendant was
OL,14,Fhanded a 12-month consecutive
OL,15,Fcustodial sentence. He was also banned
OL,16,Ffrom driving for a further 18 months,
OL,17,Fmaking a total ban of 59 months.
